@itsneekeetah 
for meditation literally all i did is sit down with my eyes closed and wait. There isnt any special trick that I know of. I did find it helpful to adhere to a rigid schedule of always meditating at 10pm because it helped with awareness in general throughout the day because i had to be aware of my rigid schedule. Whether that helps for other people I dont know. 

i think the reason meditation is helpful is that it slows down the processes of the mind so they become easier to examine. Kind of like putting a video on 0.5x speed.
